  },
  {
    question: "Can I use quizzes for lead generation?",
    answer: "<p>Yes! Quizzes are excellent for lead generation. You can require an email address before showing results, or gate the results behind a contact form. Quiz participants are highly engaged leads.</p>"
  },
  {
    question: "What types of quiz questions can I create?",
    answer: "<p>You can create multiple choice, true/false, image-based questions, and more. Each question type supports automatic scoring and custom feedback for correct and incorrect answers.</p>"
  },
  {
    question: "Can participants see their results immediately?",
    answer: "<p>You control when and how results are shown. Display scores immediately after completion, show correct answers with explanations, or send results via email. It's completely customizable.</p>"
  },
  {
    question: "Is there a limit on quiz participants?",
    answer: "<p>Response limits depend on your plan. All paid plans offer generous response allowances, and you can always upgrade if you need more capacity for larger audiences.</p>"
  }
